/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "BC_InnerAdjust" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "BC_InnerAdjust"
(
"InnerAdjustID" NUMBER(32) not null,
BCID NUMBER(32),
"StoreyID" NUMBER(32),
"FromBoothID" NUMBER(32),
"FromBoothCode" VARCHAR(20),
"FromContractCode" VARCHAR(20),
"AdjustReason" NVARCHAR2(500),
"ToBoothID" NUMBER(32),
"ToBoothCode" VARCHAR(20),
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP,
"Status" INTEGER,
"IsAbolish" INTEGER,
"UpdateTime" TIMESTAMP,
"AdjustType" INTEGER,
constraint PK_BC_INNERADJUST primary key ("InnerAdjustID")
);

comment on column "BC_InnerAdjust"."Status" is
'拟内部调整
合同创建
已取消（合同取消）
已有效（合同生效）
已废除（方案废除）';

comment on column "BC_InnerAdjust"."AdjustType" is
'10：内部调整
20：撤场
30：空场';

alter table "BC_InnerAdjust"
add constraint FK_BC_INNER_REFERENCE_BC_BOOTH foreign key (BCID)
references "BC_BoothChange" (BCID);
